										<img src="../../page_elements/content_bullet.gif" width="5" height="5"> <a href="../../../brigata/pampinea.php">Pampinea</a>: <a href="../../../texts/DecShowText.php?lang=eng&myID=nov0602&expand=day06">Sixth Day, Second Tale</a> (Cisti the baker wins the friendship of Geri Spina with good wine and a quick remark)<br>
										<img src="../../page_elements/content_bullet.gif" width="5" height="5"> <a href="../../../brigata/lauretta.php">Lauretta</a>: <a href="../../../texts/DecShowText.php?lang=eng&myID=nov0603&expand=day06">Sixth Day, Third Tale</a> (Monna Nonna replies to a jibe of the Bishop of Florence)<br>
